HEADWORD: gramma
<hw>gram"ma</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>A pasture grass of the plains of
South America and western North America; same as <er>grama grass</er>,
which see.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> grama, grama grass, gramma grass.</syn>⟦br⟧
